   <p>The <b>:target</b> CSS pseudo-class represents a unique element (the target element) with an id matching the URL's fragment. </p>
   
   <h3> Example: </h3>
   <p> Click the links to go to those paragraphs (or fragments in this case). </p>
   <div>
      <h2> Table of Contents </h2>
